[[Image:Pro Tools tempo track.png]]




'''3.''' Turn on the conductor track.




[[Image:Pro Tools conductor track in transport.png]]






'''4.''' Draw in tempo changes using the pencil tool



[[Image:Pro Tools drawing in tempo changes.png]]



